data.description: Country living in the city!! Check out this 3 Bed 2 Bath home in Midland!! This home is in a great location being just a few minutes to the kitten lake shopping area! This home features an open kitchen with large walk-in pantry, built in work area, & Spacious Dining Area! The living room is very large with a brick wood burning fireplace. Your owners suite is roomy with double closets and an ensuite bathroom featuring a double vanity sink, large tile shower, and linen closet! This home has a screened in front porch and a large yard on 1 acre of land! Turn this home into your dream home!!
